---
import HomeLayout from "../layouts/HomeLayout.astro";
---

<HomeLayout title="Ævyndal" description="Forty years ago someone wanted to know what was outside the dungeon. The world that question built is yours now.">

  <!-- NAV handled by HomeLayout -->

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Grimwell Studio · An Original Universe</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Forty years ago<br/>I wanted to know<br/>what was <em>outside<br/>the dungeon.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-hook">I'm still finding out. <strong>Now so can you.</strong></p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#enter" class="btn-primary">Begin Your Story</a>
        <a href="#ages" class="btn-ghost">Explore the World</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- AGES -->
  <section class="section" id="ages">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Eight Ages</h2>
        <div class="section-rule"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="section-sub">One world. Eight epochs. Each carries its own genre, its own relationship to magic, its own version of what survival costs. The Fourth Age is open now.</p>
      <div class="ages-grid">
        <div class="age-card locked">
          <div class="age-num">First Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Age of Creation</div>
          <div class="age-genre">Mythic fantasy. The world is new. The divine is recent. Nothing is yet inevitable.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="age-card locked">
          <div class="age-num">Second Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Chaos &amp; God-Kings</div>
          <div class="age-genre">Sword &amp; sandal. Grit, cults, barbarism, tribes, and ancient beliefs under powers no one fully understands.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="age-card locked">
          <div class="age-num">Third Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Expansion of Empires</div>
          <div class="age-genre">High fantasy. Kingdoms, borders, conquest, and the politics of power at its most dangerous.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="age-card open">
          <div class="age-open-mark">Open Now</div>
          <div class="age-num">Fourth Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Age of Exploration</div>
          <div class="age-genre">Dark fantasy. Civilizations expand to dominate the landscape. Politics, epic quests, and cults rising in the shadows of an ancient world that left more behind than anyone fully understands.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="age-card locked">
          <div class="age-num">Fifth Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Fall of the Gods</div>
          <div class="age-genre">The divine infrastructure collapses. Faith without institution. What remains when the gods stop answering?</div>
        </div>
        <div class="age-card locked">
          <div class="age-num">Sixth Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Rise of Science</div>
          <div class="age-genre">Industrial to near-future. The tension between elemental physics and a world that no longer needs to believe.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="age-card locked">
          <div class="age-num">Seventh Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Rise of the Syndicate</div>
          <div class="age-genre">Cyberpunk. Corporate power structures. Magic underground. The cost of survival in a world owned by someone else.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="age-card locked">
          <div class="age-num">Eighth Age</div>
          <div class="age-name">Dawn of Hope</div>
          <div class="age-genre">Brightpunk. Ecology, faith, and technology rewoven. A world that has been broken before — and is trying again.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- WORLDS -->
  <section class="section" id="worlds">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Worlds</h2>
        <div class="section-rule"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="section-sub">Sythlia's creation spans more than one world. The ages run through all of it.</p>
      <div class="worlds-grid">
        <div class="world-card">
          <div class="world-card-eye">Primary World · Active</div>
          <div class="world-card-name">Elydris</div>
          <div class="world-card-desc">The planet. Three continents shaped and reshaped by tectonic drift across the ages. Local star: Aryos. All current content originates here.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="world-card locked">
          <div class="world-card-eye">Secondary World · Locked</div>
          <div class="world-card-name">Felwiddel</div>
          <div class="world-card-desc">Planet of fey. Fey exist throughout Sythlia's creation, but nowhere are they more concentrated than here. Not yet available.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sub-head">
        <span class="sub-head-title">Continents of Elydris</span>
      </div>
      <div class="continents-grid">
        <div class="continent-card">
          <div class="continent-card-label">Primary Continent · Active</div>
          <div class="continent-card-name">Erinnal</div>
          <div class="continent-card-meta">43 countries · The home of adventure and the birthplace of the setting</div>
        </div>
        <div class="continent-card locked">
          <div class="continent-card-label">Second Continent · Locked</div>
          <div class="continent-card-name">Majri'dal</div>
          <div class="continent-card-meta">23 countries · Named, real, not yet available</div>
        </div>
        <div class="continent-card reserved">
          <div class="continent-card-label">Third Continent · Reserved</div>
          <div class="continent-card-name">Aris</div>
          <div class="continent-card-meta">The long destination · Available when the world is ready for it</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- LINEAGES -->
  <section class="section" id="lineages">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 class="section-title">Thirty-Three Peoples</h2>
        <div class="section-rule"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="section-sub">No elves. No dwarves. No borrowed mythology. Thirty-three original peoples in seven families, each with their own origins, their own history, their own relationship to the eight elements.</p>
      <div class="lineage-grid">
        <div class="family-card">
          <div class="family-name">Th'il</div>
          <div class="family-peoples">Adri'il · Fayd'il · Lithar'il · Myrad'il · Ryal'il · Slindar'il · Theran'il · Vaud'il</div>
          <span class="family-tag">8 Peoples</span>
        </div>
        <div class="family-card">
          <div class="family-name">Dranorvauri</div>
          <div class="family-peoples">Gnome · Gol · Guelt · Igyrlin · Karuun · Tirfolk</div>
          <span class="family-tag">6 Peoples</span>
        </div>
        <div class="family-card">
          <div class="family-name">Children of the Italti</div>
          <div class="family-peoples">Geraki · Korva'dan · Maraki · Odoko · Quirrin · Sadrath</div>
          <span class="family-tag">6 Peoples · Korva'dan available</span>
        </div>
        <div class="family-card">
          <div class="family-name">Klane</div>
          <div class="family-peoples">Human · Umbran · Vivashan</div>
          <span class="family-tag">3 Peoples</span>
        </div>
        <div class="family-card">
          <div class="family-name">Evolved</div>
          <div class="family-peoples">Gulvani · Thiraf · Värul</div>
          <span class="family-tag">3 Peoples</span>
        </div>
        <div class="family-card">
          <div class="family-name">Children of the Dreg'n</div>
          <div class="family-peoples">Goblin · Kobold · Kotera · T'nao</div>
          <span class="family-tag">4 Peoples</span>
        </div>
        <div class="family-card">
          <div class="family-name">Wrought</div>
          <div class="family-peoples">Rech · Sheydra · Fifth Age Automaton</div>
          <span class="family-tag">3 Peoples</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- VOTE -->
  <section class="vote">
    <div class="vote-inner">
      <p class="vote-eye">Community · What Opens Next</p>
      <h2 class="vote-title">The world grows in response to its inhabitants.</h2>
      <p class="vote-desc">Seven ages are locked. Two continents are waiting. You decide what opens next. Every sprint is driven by the people who live here.</p>
      <div class="vote-opts">
        <label class="vote-opt">
          <input type="radio" name="vote" value="age2" />
          <span class="vote-opt-name">Second Age</span>
          <span class="vote-opt-genre">Chaos &amp; God-Kings</span>
        </label>
        <label class="vote-opt">
          <input type="radio" name="vote" value="age3" />
          <span class="vote-opt-name">Third Age</span>
          <span class="vote-opt-genre">Expansion of Empires</span>
        </label>
        <label class="vote-opt">
          <input type="radio" name="vote" value="majridal" />
          <span class="vote-opt-name">Majri'dal</span>
          <span class="vote-opt-genre">Second Continent</span>
        </label>
      </div>
      <a href="#enter" class="btn-primary">Vote &amp; Join the List</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MAILING LIST -->
  <section class="ml" id="enter">
    <div class="ml-inner">
      <div class="ml-mark">✦</div>
      <h2 class="ml-title">You never have to start over again.</h2>
      <p class="ml-desc">Ævyndal solves the experienced GM's grief over worlds that die with campaigns. Your characters, your communities, your stories — they persist here. Be here when the next door opens.</p>
      <form
        action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/sjvox"
        method="post"
        class="ml-form"
      >
        <label for="bd-email" class="sr-only">Your email address</label>
        <input class="ml-input" type="email" name="email" id="bd-email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
        <button class="ml-btn" type="submit">Enter</button>
      </form>
      <p class="ml-note">No noise. Only when something opens.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <span class="footer-mark">Ævyndal</span>
    <nav class="footer-nav">
      <a href="https://evindale.com/atlas">Atlas</a>
      <span>·</span>
      <a href="https://evindale.com/gods">Deities</a>
      <span>·</span>
      <a href="https://evindale.com/lineages">Lineages</a>
      <span>·</span>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/kZetsKk">Discord</a>
    </nav>
    <span class="footer-copy">© SJ Kraus</span>
  </footer>

</HomeLayout>

<style>
  :root {
    --void:          #09080A;
    --ink:           #1A1614;
    --haze:          #2E2926;
    --fog:           #3A3530;
    --ash:           #5C5650;
    --bone-dim:      #8A837A;
    --bone:          #D0C9BC;
    --threat:        #8B3218;
    --glow:          #C4501E;
    --font-display:  'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    --font-body:     'Lora', Georgia, serif;
  }

  /* ═══ HERO ═══ */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 0 3rem 7rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%; right: 5%;
    width: 55vw; height: 100vh;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 70% at 60% 30%,
      rgba(196,80,30,0.18) 0%,
      rgba(139,50,24,0.08) 40%,
      transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 30vh;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--void) 0%, transparent 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 740px; }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--glow);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 0.9s ease forwards 0.3s;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.0;
    color: var(--bone);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 1s ease forwards 0.5s;
  }
  .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--bone-dim); }
  .hero-hook {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ash);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 1s ease forwards 0.7s;
  }
  .hero-hook strong { color: var(--bone); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 1s ease forwards 0.9s;
  }

  @keyframes rise {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ═══ BUTTONS ═══ */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.8rem;
    background: var(--threat);
    color: var(--bone);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--glow);
    transition: background 0.25s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--glow); }
  .btn-ghost {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fog);
    padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
    transition: color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--bone); border-color: var(--ash); }

  /* ═══ DIVIDER ═══ */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    margin: 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--threat), transparent);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* ═══ SECTIONS ═══ */
  .section { padding: 6rem 3rem; }
  .section-inner { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bone);
    line-height: 1;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .section-rule { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--fog); }
  .section-sub {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ═══ AGES ═══ */
  .ages-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--fog);
    border: 1px solid var(--fog);
  }
  .age-card {
    background: var(--void);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.3rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.25s;
  }
  .age-card:hover { background: var(--ink); }
  .age-card.open { background: var(--ink); border-top: 2px solid var(--glow); }
  .age-card.locked { opacity: 0.55; }
  .age-card.locked:hover { opacity: 0.75; }
  .age-num {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .age-card.open .age-num { color: var(--glow); }
  .age-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bone);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .age-genre {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .age-card.open .age-genre { color: var(--bone-dim); }
  .age-open-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.8rem; right: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 0.52rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--glow);
    border: 1px solid var(--threat);
    padding: 0.18rem 0.45rem;
  }

  /* ═══ WORLDS ═══ */
  .worlds-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--fog);
    border: 1px solid var(--fog);
    margin-bottom: 1px;
  }
  .continents-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--fog);
    border: 1px solid var(--fog);
    border-top: none;
  }
  .world-card {
    background: var(--void);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.6rem;
    transition: background 0.25s;
  }
  .world-card:hover { background: var(--ink); }
  .world-card.locked { opacity: 0.5; }
  .world-card-eye {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .world-card-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--glow);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .world-card.locked .world-card-name { color: var(--ash); }
  .world-card-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ash); line-height: 1.6; }
  .continent-card {
    background: var(--void);
    padding: 1.3rem 1.5rem;
    transition: background 0.25s;
  }
  .continent-card:hover { background: var(--ink); }
  .continent-card.locked { opacity: 0.5; }
  .continent-card.reserved { opacity: 0.35; }
  .continent-card-label {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .continent-card-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--glow);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .continent-card.locked .continent-card-name { color: var(--ash); }
  .continent-card.reserved .continent-card-name { color: var(--fog); }
  .continent-card-meta { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--ash); font-style: italic; }
  .sub-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 3rem 0 0;
    padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fog);
  }
  .sub-head-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bone-dim);
  }

  /* ═══ LINEAGES ═══ */
  .lineage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--fog);
    border: 1px solid var(--fog);
  }
  .family-card {
    background: var(--void);
    padding: 1.3rem 1.4rem;
    transition: background 0.25s;
  }
  .family-card:hover { background: var(--ink); }
  .family-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bone);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .family-peoples { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ash); line-height: 1.75; }
  .family-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.56rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--glow);
    border: 1px solid var(--threat);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.45rem;
  }

  /* ═══ VOTE ═══ */
  .vote {
    padding: 6rem 3rem;
    background: var(--ink);
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .vote::before, .vote::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--threat), transparent);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .vote::before { top: 0; }
  .vote::after  { bottom: 0; }
  .vote-inner { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .vote-eye {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--glow);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .vote-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bone);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .vote-desc { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--ash); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .vote-opts {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--fog);
    border: 1px solid var(--fog);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .vote-opt {
    background: var(--void);
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .vote-opt:hover { background: var(--haze); }
  .vote-opt input { display: none; }
  .vote-opt-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bone);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }
  .vote-opt-genre { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--ash); font-style: italic; }

  /* ═══ MAILING LIST ═══ */
  .ml { padding: 7rem 3rem; text-align: center; }
  .ml-inner { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ml-mark {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--threat);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ml-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bone);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .ml-desc { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--ash); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .ml-form { display: flex; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ml-input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.1rem;
    background: var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--fog);
    border-right: none;
    color: var(--bone);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    outline: none;
  }
  .ml-input::placeholder { color: var(--ash); }
